endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;我们知道，中东战争导致油价飙升后，电动汽车列表的在线搜索量有所增加。现在，有关冲突影响的硬数据开始逐渐涌现。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;我们今天的时事通讯着眼&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;于 3 月份英国、法国和韩国等国家的&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/mZpQEm4QrSaWMTca4Z4SAN_z9X3DVVnBulVB1y7yf2aq-i_q_7PvQfgQXv2smR1k99k3qboYT3IMrgMKD5FFMXOyKZvgby_camxGQkvGcoi9jaxMnTmC_-2dCNJZRCGEbU4-3u_t_qV4HKZ7jNgoes76Zk0QggAZGdBWstLC27YlYrWgwuQ0XALS9DeYMJCt-f5UeM4TRwgXJ1zMcyTTFA8qtAttglOlf5TXTRdStV1svBOMa868E2pOF0DNzV2bjFJXWb1FKZeVrZ3cHultEr43OPo0dIyM0pnHXbjIFVdJgH_mReS1KRU7z9JaMPSshxKzGkQVpAfjhTLcGT1iXVAPVscN0Qqii2Gxod9XUfuYNnQ6tugJFO0DeR6bsJ6AXHGZPyIUhlM14ciTfFHqg4MA8TEppm914wlRge7KNfAgcnC0dXObFzRUahD0Ff_4WSFOx0TfL2_J2Q9_-weNrnqZf1TxfHON7ttPq-WAx2IR1aYZTVPKmhnDk0xG4mK-QcQBg5IllUG_h4aMB2bLi8hq5E9-Soz6lKy1-MjnHXZoPEw/QhSWcvODIQZfnOrnR48Gku3shZfCrCHm/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;电动汽车销量如何飙升&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;与此同时，在东南亚，席卷的热浪加上节能措施使&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/w9ETfalYJWs--kG_UWQt92lgVFxcY3sZkmwfpkBaGQHn7tFBzBBVP9Sr6_DcOK3THORs_luWTZK2quMlx10y0CquICylTnGRcFUHN9vrU5RhmFGgWCs-TO5AosN8DYzVh3OzcN2aGLEdezB06e8ggDWdPHT0w5bnjEVQBFwRrDFH5C6WSpBEquxCk1YWyM0XcTpziOmFElqw45epivgEzbu0sl6jxQM2qpv8z9xXd6R0QxpCXUK8uG66eZSPpgL6atB4d3Tstt01NmZ9Db9CxULY6AK3hLRonl4vrKN4v15ZFxqTjOha56RDguCi2--JKQhC98G9OGWwy2K1rKBH6k6C0urb-lj9d17M8nTxUrKWLeQEKatb7Dh9p7usToFBCHEIgwl-OUPuTXa8LRc0tNgmeP0PIBKpbPJDbI3RWEVEPX9t-91ZVUydZHQTXCH-KRlAxJrvdvQYaA9Ag6ag5rs4OE4EHOhJWcqxZQ88Eg-jp9LeIz6y0rczNu0Yvel_5kEObjQeq9WKWCXoOB7Zif-5JXCdzfplwhLLsfC6Mycz9jdiw0FN8NKZ3XlFZNbVgw/1B4oOQxBUFX1Vbxjou1L5d3_hBilwvtw/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="东南亚上班族在节能